79
00:08:32,340 --> 00:08:38,770
That's why I brought our noble madam of Woo One here.

80
00:08:38,770 --> 00:08:43,590
Because I always start with the weakness like a hyena.

81
00:08:44,640 --> 00:08:47,510
I'm the weakness?

82
