109
00:13:28,170 --> 00:13:32,190
I'll meet up with Song Pan Ho soon and come up with a plan.

110
00:13:32,190 --> 00:13:34,340
You just stay low and wait.

111
00:13:34,340 --> 00:13:38,410
No. I'll have to meet him myself.

112
00:13:38,410 --> 00:13:41,810
Who do you think got me in this situation?

113
00:13:41,810 --> 00:13:45,490
All right, all right. I'll be in touch.

114
00:13:49,410 --> 00:13:53,940
Right. You need a whip to get a horse to move.

115
00:13:53,940 --> 00:13:55,880
My goodness...

116
