<i>Become a strong man at Good Man Gym! Recruiting new members!</i>

163
00:19:14,100 --> 00:19:17,010
<i>Good Man Gym</i>

164
00:19:21,820 --> 00:19:24,180
But still, you got a lot better.

165
00:19:24,180 --> 00:19:26,570
You're keeping up with the meal plan, right?

166
00:19:26,570 --> 00:19:28,510
You're doing great.

167
00:19:29,290 --> 00:19:32,220
- Hello! Is this your first time?
- Yes.

168
00:19:32,220 --> 00:19:36,440
These machines are mostly for your legs and these are mostly for your biceps.

169
00:19:36,440 --> 00:19:39,820
They didn't put the weights on here.

170
00:20:08,560 --> 00:20:13,140
I believe I told you it won't be good if you don't answer your phone.

171
00:20:13,140 --> 00:20:17,200
It's painful to answer that phone call.

172
00:20:27,900 --> 00:20:31,850
Just listen. I'm telling you this for your sake.

173
00:20:32,450 --> 00:20:34,300
Let go of me.

174
00:20:44,970 --> 00:20:48,040
I'll be the one presiding over Kim Sang Hyeok's trial.

175
00:20:48,040 --> 00:20:51,090
If I appear favorable to Chairman Kim Kang Heon

176
00:20:51,090 --> 00:20:53,760
and then try to release Kim Sang Hyeok with a not-guilty verdict,

177
00:20:53,760 --> 00:20:57,070
what would the court and the prosecution will think?

178
00:20:57,070 --> 00:21:00,540
There's even a video of Kim Sang Hyeok shooting the gun.

179
00:21:00,540 --> 00:21:03,750
Lee Sang Taek's son, Lee Cheong Gang, is there, too.

180
00:21:03,750 --> 00:21:06,960
There are so many hurdles right now.

181
00:21:06,960 --> 00:21:11,910
And you're telling me to look like Chairman Kim Gang Heon's pawn?

182
00:21:12,610 --> 00:21:17,550
The evidence used to detain Chairman Kim's wife is too sloppy to be used in the trial.

183
00:21:17,550 --> 00:21:19,390
She'll be released anyway.

184
00:21:19,390 --> 00:21:24,940
Are you saying we mess up what we need to do over something so simple?

185
00:21:27,240 --> 00:21:31,040
Even if he's the chairman of Woo One,

186
00:21:31,040 --> 00:21:33,660
there are things he can't do.

187
00:21:36,270 --> 00:21:38,590
If he...

188
00:21:38,590 --> 00:21:41,170
If he can really do anything,

189
00:21:41,170 --> 00:21:44,710
tell him to kill me and do it himself.

190
00:21:45,410 --> 00:21:47,310
When you're at my age,

191
00:21:47,310 --> 00:21:50,460
hanging onto my life doesn't matter that much.

192
00:21:50,460 --> 00:21:55,430
Things like pride and conviction become even more important.

193
00:22:05,720 --> 00:22:09,620
Though I should drag you to Chairman right now,

194
00:22:10,410 --> 00:22:13,380
let's wrap things up here. Instead...

195
00:22:13,990 --> 00:22:17,410
be there tomorrow morning. If you don't...

196
00:22:18,090 --> 00:22:20,150
you'll die.

197
00:23:01,650 --> 00:23:04,420
<i>Good Man Gym</i>

198
00:23:34,070 --> 00:23:37,520
Hey, it's me. Tomorrow at 1:00 p.m.

199
00:23:37,520 --> 00:23:42,060
The location is a restaurant called Cheongwoo House at the outer beach of Woowon City.

200
00:23:42,060 --> 00:23:44,090
I'll see you there.

201
00:24:37,070 --> 00:24:39,650
Did you say you don't care if you die?

202
00:24:42,340 --> 00:24:44,630
Yes, just kill me.

203
00:24:44,630 --> 00:24:48,250
Rather, I can also turn myself in as

204
00:24:48,250 --> 00:24:51,330
the hit-and-run incident's real culprit.

205
00:24:52,020 --> 00:24:55,830
Because you'll lose the trial anyway if you keep this up.

206
00:24:55,830 --> 00:24:59,710
If that happens, I'm a dead man anyway.

207
00:24:59,710 --> 00:25:04,900
So, it'd be better to die proudly than to die shamefully.

208
00:25:26,980 --> 00:25:31,050
I-If I die, you can't get your son out.

209
00:25:31,050 --> 00:25:33,100
It doesn't matter.

210
00:25:33,100 --> 00:25:38,000
Just as you take life lightly, I take it lightly as well.

211
00:25:54,740 --> 00:25:57,200
So, your ego was bruised?

212
00:26:01,670 --> 00:26:06,220
You have the luxury to say your ego was bruised?

213
00:26:06,790 --> 00:26:11,200
Do you want me to give you the same pain I feel?

214
00:26:11,200 --> 00:26:13,950
Will you still be talking about your ego?

215
00:26:13,950 --> 00:26:16,150
Do you think you can?

216
00:27:00,490 --> 00:27:03,930
As of now, I've determined that the evidence

217
00:27:03,930 --> 00:27:07,230
Prosecutor Kang So Yeong submitted isn't enough to prove

218
00:27:07,230 --> 00:27:10,090
Ma Ji Yeong's instigated murder and arson charges.

219
00:27:10,090 --> 00:27:14,160
As such, an arrest seems unnecessary to me.

220
00:27:14,160 --> 00:27:17,330
Yes, you made the right determination.

221
00:27:17,330 --> 00:27:19,550
It's all good.

222
00:27:19,550 --> 00:27:23,410
I'll send it to the prosecution and take care of it today.

223
00:27:25,490 --> 00:27:27,670
<i>Chairman Kim Kang Heon</i>

224
00:27:36,030 --> 00:27:37,610
It was resolved.

225
00:27:37,610 --> 00:27:41,550
The detention center said they'll let her go once the paperwork is completed.

226
00:27:41,550 --> 00:27:43,210
All right.

227
00:27:51,250 --> 00:27:54,700
<i>Case number 1673.</i>

228
00:27:54,700 --> 00:27:57,220
What time is Ms. Ma Ji Yeong getting released?

229
00:27:57,220 --> 00:27:59,350
1:30 p.m.?

230
00:28:00,010 --> 00:28:03,250
Got it. Yes, thank you.

231
00:28:21,580 --> 00:28:24,250
Hello, Judge Song.

232
00:28:24,250 --> 00:28:26,080
Are you going somewhere?

233
00:28:26,720 --> 00:28:29,280
I'm going to the gym.

234
00:29:10,620 --> 00:29:12,810
We've got exactly 30 minutes.

235
00:29:12,810 --> 00:29:16,410
After we talk, I'll go back to my office right away.

236
00:29:17,550 --> 00:29:20,230
Yes, I'll see you there.

237
00:29:21,310 --> 00:29:24,410
<i>Jeong Yi Hwa</i>

238
00:29:55,610 --> 00:29:57,840
Let's go to Sang Hyeon.

239
